  #PositionPlacement +0p +2106p

Style "URxvt" Colorset 1, HilightColorset 1, BorderColorset 1, HilightBorderColorset 3
Style "Emacs" Colorset 1, HilightColorset 1, BorderColorset 1, HilightBorderColorset 3
